{"tid":2331146,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[最新宣誓] 林鄭敦促公務員 : 不僅是遵守，而是更須支持、推廣、信奉《基本法》!","createTime":"2020-12-18T14:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T17:45:45.000Z","uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"52da1e554b1a55d45141016849e099d1a940b1e6","tid":2331146,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BBtnwlYGJigq9eNylKh-Gj98jaI=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JRZTB3QEBJCCVDJ3R2MJBUA2AY.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBBtnwlYGJigq9eNylKh-Gj98jaI%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJRZTB3QEBJCCVDJ3R2MJBUA2AY.jpeg&h=cc1f0eba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼日前副局長和政治助理宣誓後，各政策局的常任秘書長和部門首長等，今日亦在特首林鄭月娥見證下，宣誓擁護《基本法》和效忠香港特區。林鄭致辭時稱，公務員宣誓可「確保香港特區政府有效管治」，又<span class=\"red\">敦促公務員「支持、推廣和信奉《基本法》」</span>另外，今日宣誓的站位安排，仍沿用上次被親建制報章質疑的站位安排，林鄭居中而站，而且比兩旁的張建宗及聶德權站前約一步。<br />\n<br />\n港府發出的新聞稿指，今日宣誓的公僕包括常秘、部門首長及首長級薪級表第6點（D6）或以上的公務員，眾人由公務員事務局常秘楊何蓓茵帶領宣誓。出席的除了負責監誓的林鄭外，亦有政務司司長張建宗和公務員事務局局長聶德權。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在儀式上致辭稱，<span class=\"red\">要求公僕宣誓和簽署聲明，可加強公務員「明確知道自己公職身份所帶來責任的意識和真切體現國家以及社會對於特區政府公務員的要求」，並且「進一步保護、鞏固和推廣公務員隊伍須恪守的核心價值，從而確保香港特區政府有效管治。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0fEClgvcH9nMABOIBmMdD7mfF_4=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TXXE76HQV5BB5NUQR5ZMSQGHBE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0fEClgvcH9nMABOIBmMdD7mfF_4%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTXXE76HQV5BB5NUQR5ZMSQGHBE.JPG&h=4d8e9f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭又要求一眾今日宣誓的公僕「<span class=\"red\">以身作則，為全體公務員樹立良好榜樣」，在日常工作中體現擁護《基本法》和效忠香港特區的莊嚴承諾，同時謹記「擁護《基本法》不是僅僅為了遵守《基本法》，而是更須支持、推廣和信奉《基本法》」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>沿用被指「企錯位」安排 令人錯覺官員宣誓效忠林鄭</strong><br />\n另外，今日公務員宣誓儀式的站位，沿用日前副局政助宣誓時的站位安排，即林鄭站在印有國旗區旗的背景板前中間位置，面向宣誓的官員，而宣誓的官員則排列成矩形及面向林鄭。<br />\n<br />\n有關的站位安排，日前被《星島》專欄文章引述「熟識內地官方儀式」人士質疑「企錯位」，因國務院總理李克強為官員監誓時是站在側面，宣誓的官員是面向國徽國旗宣誓，故林鄭的站位「令人有官員向她（林鄭月娥）宣誓效忠的錯覺。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201218/CCKLCRDPBZEC7D2EUHGQ6J4CDE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0SbP5oiRfFy4IRAzw7yKAU9bws86c9NFdcoTaivhe1F7FLwOOtHI1Va_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201218%2FCCKLCRDPBZEC7D2EUHGQ6J4CDE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0SbP5oiRfFy4IRAzw7yKAU9bws86c9NFdcoTaivhe1F7FLwOOtHI1Va_M&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBfvW7D1Q%2FvztR01HWodNoCE%3D&h=b5f7e76a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201218%2FCCKLCRDPBZEC7D2EUHGQ6J4CDE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0SbP5oiRfFy4IRAzw7yKAU9bws86c9NFdcoTaivhe1F7FLwOOtHI1Va_M&h=3c7f0f91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201218/CCKLCRDPBZEC7D2EUHGQ6J4CDE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0SbP5oiRfFy4IRAzw7yKAU9bws86c9NFdcoTaivhe1F7FLwOOtHI1Va_M</a>"},{"pid":"b6e440a9fcc5dc0d97e8a747aedd75fafabfcace","tid":2331146,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44413be41984d5a4c02913aff987b097b544621c","tid":2331146,"uid":35930,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"基本法係宗教？"},{"pid":"d5de85ea85d0705819fa28e3b